## New data model

### `dumps` table (unchanged)

```
id           uuid pk
user_id      uuid fk users
text         text
created_at   timestamptz
```

### `actionables` table (replaces preps)

```
id              uuid pk
user_id         uuid fk users
dump_id         uuid fk dumps
text            text        -- the extracted thought, clean and short
original_text   text        -- raw fragment from dump that produced this
status          enum        -- 'inbox' | 'done' | 'snoozed' | 'dismissed'
tone            enum        -- 'confident' | 'tentative' | 'idea' | 'someday'
urgency         enum        -- 'today' | 'this_week' | 'someday' | 'none'
batch_key       text        -- nullable. 'shopping' | 'errands' | 'follow_ups' | null
due_at          timestamptz -- nullable. exact datetime if detected
period_start    timestamptz -- nullable. for period-based timing (e.g. start of weekend)
period_end      timestamptz -- nullable. for period-based timing (e.g. end of weekend)
period_label    text        -- nullable. 'weekend' | 'this week' | 'next week' | 'morning' | etc.
timezone_pending boolean    -- true if extracted before user timezone was known
snoozed_until   timestamptz -- nullable. set when status = snoozed
done_at         timestamptz -- nullable
dismissed_at    timestamptz -- nullable
created_at      timestamptz
updated_at      timestamptz
```

No calendar fields. Calendar is not in scope for iteration 1.

### Journal / “Thoughts” screen (no separate `thoughts` table)

Raw input is **`dumps.text`**; polished copy is **`dumps.polished_text`**. List + detail for the hub **Thoughts** tab use **`GET /dumps`** and **`GET /dumps/:id`** (mobile route path can still be `/thoughts` for the tab label only).

